Extension này chạy trên **Chrome Extension Manifest V3 (MV3)** — chuẩn mới nhất của Google Chrome kể từ 2023.

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Chrome Extension (711 KiB)"
        SP[🖥️ Side Panel UI\nReact/Vanilla JS\nHTMLCSS]
        SW[⚙️ Service Worker\nBackground Logic\nQueue Manager]
        CS[💉 Content Script\nDOM Automation\nlabs.google.com]
        MP[📨 Message Passing\nchrome.runtime API]
    end

    subgraph "Target Website"
        GF[🌐 Google Flow\nlabs.google.com/fx/tools/flow]
        DOM[📄 DOM Elements\nInput, Buttons\nVideo Players]
    end

    subgraph "Chrome APIs"
        DL[📥 chrome.downloads]
        TABS[🗂️ chrome.tabs]
        ST[💾 chrome.storage]
        I18N[🌐 chrome.i18n]
    end

    SP <-->|Messages| SW
    SW <-->|chrome.tabs.sendMessage| CS
    CS <-->|Manipulate| DOM
    DOM -->|From| GF
    SW -->|Trigger| DL
    SW -->|Monitor| TABS
    SW <-->|Persist Queue| ST
    SP -->|Display lang| I18N
```

