## VIII. 🔄 Luồng Dữ Liệu Hoàn Chỉnh (End-to-End Flow)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant SidePanel as 🖥️ Side Panel
    participant SW as ⚙️ Service Worker
    participant CS as 💉 Content Script
    participant GF as 🌐 Google Flow DOM
    participant DL as 📥 chrome.downloads

    User->>SidePanel: Paste 10 prompts, click Run
    SidePanel->>SW: sendMessage(ADD_JOBS, jobs[])
    SW->>SW: Khởi tạo QueueManager với 10 jobs

    loop Với mỗi job (concurrency: 2)
        SW->>CS: sendMessage(CREATE_AND_RUN_PROMPT)
        CS->>GF: Click "New Project"
        CS->>GF: Set prompt text (React synthetic event)
        CS->>GF: Select Model (Veo 3.1 Fast)
        CS->>GF: Click Generate button
        CS->>GF: Poll status mỗi 2 giây...
        GF-->>CS: Video URL ready!
        CS->>CS: Extract last frame URL
        CS-->>SW: {success, videoUrl, lastImage}
        SW->>DL: chrome.downloads.download(videoUrl)
        SW->>SidePanel: notifyPanel(job_completed)
        SidePanel->>User: Update progress bar ✅
        SW->>SW: Feed lastImage vào job tiếp theo (chaining!)
    end

    SW->>SidePanel: All done! 10/10 videos completed
```

